{"tid":681360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人搭飛機在商務艙偷走17萬","createTime":"2018-05-28T03:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T09:37:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":108,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b66ee7e565c9687f459ae7f4e48deecac55d212e","tid":681360,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2439038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2439038&d=svrvB11%2FOjkRJrQQYRknZ7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ee52be6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2439038&h=4e617362\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2439038</a><br />\n<br />\n中客的品質讓世界各國頻頻搖頭，如今竟然連搭飛機也能犯罪。有泰國導遊在臉書透露，她帶隊坐飛機到日本時，商務艙客戶的64萬日元現鈔（約新台幣17萬元）竟然不翼而飛，一查之下才知道是附近座位的中國人偷的！<br />\n<br />\n泰國導遊BackpacKiks表示，26日帶團時有商務艙乘客在飛機上被偷了錢，抵達日本後航空公司禁止任何人離開，並由警方登機辦案。導遊說，被竊的乘客是把錢放在頭上的置物箱裡，警方在調查時，發現坐在旁邊的中國旅客有異，一搜之下發現中國人在座椅上藏了很多錢。<br />\n<br />\n泰國人Karn Chivangkun也在臉書轉貼照片，指出搭機旅行在睡覺的時候，應該將錢貼身保管，不要放在頭頂的行李櫃。BackpacKiks說，其實案發後有乘客表示，看到該名中國嫌犯多次走來走去形跡可疑，她建議民眾每次下機時，應該都要檢查貴重物品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpIrDK4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpIrDK4g.jpg&h=e445a023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php7JVAL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php7JVAL3.jpg&h=cddde1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpvRsYJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpvRsYJ4.jpg&h=1dbfa0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZB0glF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZB0glF.jpg&h=1e6d1fba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"038e37820187aa2c5463aa25a84dd1ea9f187972","tid":681360,"uid":22736,"like":222,"dislike":0,"score":222,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"中國只有賊同騙子是真的"},{"pid":"e08f56583a04ccee95d23d3a1565536107f7c9f6","tid":681360,"uid":128603,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a7587ff6c36903802baafe7ca6be788f47a5ee","tid":681360,"uid":57410,"like":4,"dislike":330,"score":-326,"quote":{"pid":"038e37820187aa2c5463aa25a84dd1ea9f187972","tid":681360,"uid":22736,"like":222,"dislike":0,"score":222,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"中國只有賊同騙子是真的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"突然間反思你呢種留言懶係有共嗚 實質毫無養份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 5毛"},{"pid":"9fbab9cd1444d85f058441d9f7100e4b3903d269","tid":681360,"uid":3457,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"真係蠢 <br />\n分少少比其他人喇17萬 咁咪唔洗比人拉囉 <br />\n中國都係咁嫁喇"},{"pid":"c81462ab5410ae355cf152f77bf668262988b840","tid":681360,"uid":103317,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9fbab9cd1444d85f058441d9f7100e4b3903d269","tid":681360,"uid":3457,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"真係蠢 <br />\n分少少比其他人喇17萬 咁咪唔洗比人拉囉 <br />\n中國都係咁嫁喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"偷幾張咪冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁貪"},{"pid":"5bb7e1480cf35b1fcf8f78dcbdaaa0246547b71f","tid":681360,"uid":23635,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"做乜咁唔愛国？要去日本玩，仲要偷錢俾人拉，真係柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc1461c8ee2c241a6ab7f523297b0584370e28f","tid":681360,"uid":5